01:01:47.540 --> 01:01:50.660
It is transferring momentum from the cord to you.


01:01:50.660 --> 01:01:53.340
It's an alias to a whip action.


01:01:53.340 --> 01:01:56.340
And the net effect is that you accelerate faster


01:01:56.340 --> 01:01:59.700
than gravity because the cord is actually pulling you down.


01:01:59.700 --> 01:02:03.500
It turns out that the difference you would be off by


01:02:03.500 --> 01:02:05.280
